sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant H as Tracking hooks
    participant B as useBehaviorTracker<br/>(in-memory buffer)
    participant R as useReadinessSignals<br/>(threshold evaluator)
    participant UI as Advisor surface

    U->>H: hover, scroll, view reviews
    H->>B: push event
    B->>B: aggregate per product
    B->>R: read current state
    R->>R: evaluate thresholds<br/>(dwell, scroll, comparison)
    alt thresholds met
        R->>UI: enable breathing button<br/>or contextual chip
    else thresholds not met
        R->>UI: idle
    end
    U->>UI: click (user-initiated)
    UI->>U: open advisor
